  "original_title": "Thriposha distribution underway for mothers",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Thriposha distribution underway for mothers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Thriposha Ltd announced that it commenced distributing Thriposha to all beneficiaries including all pregnant mothers and all breastfeeding mothers ( Up to the completion of 06 months for the infant) who are undergoing nutritious requirements.",
        "Sri Lanka Thriposha Ltd Deepthi Kularatna speaking to News 1st that 850,000 Triposha packets have been distributed, however, Triposha for children is yet to be delivered.",
        "Deepthi Kularatna said that due to the shortage of maize and soybean it has become impossible to streamline the production of Triposha in the country.",
        "However, he said that agreements will be inked with suppliers to import Maize and Soy beans under the Indian Credit Line.",
        "He further said that steps will be taken to produce Thriposha for children as well.",
        "However, he said that due to the shortage of fuel, problems have arisen in the distribution of triposha."
      ],
